<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q40_v10" title="Q40_v10" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>Dos plataformas de arriendo de películas, CinePlus y PeliMax, cobran en función de la cantidad de películas <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi></m:math> que un usuario alquila en un mes.</p>
    <p>Para CinePlus, el costo total, en pesos, se calcula como 
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>C</m:mi>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mn>900</m:mn>
        <m:mo>+</m:mo>
        <m:mn>300</m:mn>
        <m:mo>·</m:mo>
        <m:mi>n</m:mi>
      </m:math>.
    </p>
    <p>Para PeliMax, el costo total, en pesos, se calcula como 
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>C</m:mi>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mi>b</m:mi>
        <m:mo>+</m:mo>
        <m:mn>250</m:mn>
        <m:mo>·</m:mo>
        <m:mi>n</m:mi>
      </m:math>.
    </p>
    <p>Si un usuario alquila <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> películas en un mes y el costo total es el mismo en ambas plataformas, ¿cuál debe ser el valor de la suscripción de PeliMax, en pesos?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>¿Cuál debe ser el valor de la suscripción de PeliMax?</qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">400<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>400</m:mn></m:math>, entonces en PeliMax el costo para <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> es <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>400</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>400</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;400</m:mn></m:math>. Pero en CinePlus el costo es <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;400</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>2&#160;400</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>, esta opción no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">1300<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! En CinePlus, para <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>, el costo es <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;400</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces en PeliMax debe cumplirse <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>, es decir, <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>. Al despejar, <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">3300<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>, entonces en PeliMax el costo para <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> es <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>. En CinePlus, para <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>, el costo es <m:math><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>5&#160;300</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>, esta opción no cumple la condición de igualdad de costos.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">5300<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>, entonces en PeliMax el costo para <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> es <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5&#160;300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5&#160;300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>. En CinePlus, para <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>, el costo es <m:math><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>7&#160;300</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn></m:math>, esta opción no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Calcular el costo en CinePlus para 8 películas</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión de CinePlus es <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mi>n</m:mi></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Como el usuario alquila <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> películas, reemplazamos:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;400</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Expresar el costo en PeliMax para 8 películas</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión de PeliMax es <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mi>n</m:mi></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Reemplazando <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;000</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Igualar ambos costos</strong></p>
            <p>El enunciado dice que el costo total es el mismo en ambas plataformas, por lo tanto:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Despejar el valor de la suscripción</strong></p>
            <p>Restamos <m:math><m:mn>2&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> en ambos lados:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3&#160;300</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;000</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1&#160;300</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La suscripción de PeliMax debe ser de <m:math><m:mn>1&#160;300</m:mn></m:math> pesos.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>